The paper is about Online Learning to Rank (OLTR) methods, which are commonly used in Information Retrieval (IR) and Machine Learning (ML) applications. Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of neural networks, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, and cs.AI.
